{"tid":989831,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"反課金人士召集區 (歡迎課金撚入黎挑機)","createTime":"2019-01-21T07:09:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-26T09:05:50.000Z","uid":17718,"like":8,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"653d1e8402a7588a5fda2ffc5db478aab7d112e1","tid":989831,"uid":17718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T07:09:34.000Z","msg":"各位, 覺唔覺得遊戲課金係一件好on9嘅事<br />\n你用錢買黎更好裝備, 更好道具, 更多遊戲幣<br />\n換黎嘅只係虛擬嘅成功同一時嘅滿足感, 自豪感同英雄感<br />\n二黎用等級壓制對手, 根本顯示唔出你嘅實力<br />\n我本身都係一個幾入迷嘅打機人士, 不過我真係完全唔鍾意課金 , 有錢都唔課<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔課金個遊戲先刺激好玩, 課金好快厭<br />\n而且屌打到課金撚時個感覺真係好撚爽皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有錢嘅話我寧願食多D好西, 去多D地方旅行, 買多D自己鍾意嘅野, 甚至過大海發下達都好, 都唔會課$1落一隻game度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a86f950056b6887c5f2bf47f5a5f223401b72e1","tid":989831,"uid":17718,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T07:12:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uPDAWww.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuPDAWww.jpg&h=7fc4bf85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我一直都玩開pad，一直奮鬥到800rank，完全冇課金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"183120d448cde90430cb813b52869c6dca8b06d2","tid":989831,"uid":134997,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T07:16:09.000Z","msg":"無人課金點經營落去呀<br />\n免費俾埋間公司你好唔好"},{"pid":"15abc371e9d290e58bbf9cadf305c37596aeeb06","tid":989831,"uid":177403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"183120d448cde90430cb813b52869c6dca8b06d2","tid":989831,"uid":134997,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T07:16:09.000Z","msg":"無人課金點經營落去呀<br />\n免費俾埋間公司你好唔好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T07:24:52.000Z","msg":"此post已完<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48710d355c63e52d7a1f68dc25e4c2c4df3bde1f","tid":989831,"uid":65587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc